          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2013-06-05T14:51:20Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Davis-Bacon Repeal Act - Repeals the Davis-Bacon Act (which requires that the locally prevailing wage rate be paid to various classes of laborers and mechanics working under federally-financed or federally-assisted contracts for construction, alteration, and repair of public buildings or public works).</p> <p>States that references in any law to a wage requirement of the Davis-Bacon Act after the enactment of this Act shall be null and void.</p> </p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <updateDate>2013-05-16T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
